title: Razia Sultan
subTitle: Razia Sultan, the first female ruler of the Delhi Sultanate, lands in trouble and loses her kingdom when she falls in love with Jamal-ud-Din Yakut, an Abyssinian slave.

title: Chalti Ka Naam Gaadi
subTitle: Brijmohan, a mechanic, swears off women after a bad experience. However, when a headstrong woman arrives at his garage, he is forced to reconsider his opinion.

title: C.I.D.
subTitle: Shrivastav attempts to expose a rich man's link to the underworld but gets killed in the process. When his friend Inspector Shekhar tries to find the killer, he himself becomes a suspect.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Bhuvan Shome
subTitle: A lonely bureaucrat goes on holiday to a village in Gujarat where a young peasant woman helps him see beyond his job and develop a newfound empathy for people.

title: Banarasi Babu
subTitle: Sohan Lal, a rich businessman, is abducted and imprisoned. When Gulabiya helps him to escape from the prison, he meets with an accident. He then attempts to sort out his jeopardised life.

title: Aashiq Hoon Baharon Ka
subTitle: Chaos ensues as Vikram, driven by greed and ego, hinders the blossoming romance between Ashok and Veera by trapping Ashok with false accusations of theft.

title: Mehboob Ki Mehndi
subTitle: Shabana is employed by Yusuf, a rich man, to teach his nephew. Eventually, Yusuf and Shabana fall in love and plan to get married. But the girl has a troubled past that may destroy her future.

title: Pukar
subTitle: Major Jaidev saves a politician from the clutches of a dreaded terrorist. However, the terrorist joins hands with his childhood friend Anjali to ruin his life.

title: Roti Kapada Aur Makaan
subTitle: Bharat, a graduate and the eldest son of a poverty-stricken family, struggles to provide for his kin after his father's retirement.

title: Tere Mere Beech Mein
subTitle: A carefree country bumpkin's simple life turns chaotic and comical when he unexpectedly inherits a fortune, leading to hilarious misadventures as he navigates wealth and its unexpected challenges.

title: Sadhu Aur Shaitaan
subTitle: Sher Khan, a criminal, decides to rob a bank. However, his life takes a dramatic turn when he meets a kind-hearted taxi driver.

title: Story Of Gauri Putra Ganesh
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Hum Do Hamare Do
subTitle: A young and hardworking man who is burdened with the responsibility of his six sisters turns down a marriage proposal from a woman who is in love with him.

title: Honeymoon
subTitle: A couple's idyllic lake honeymoon turns chaotic when the husband discovers his wife disoriented in the night, unleashing unforeseen turmoil.

title: Dil Ne Phir Yaad Kiya
subTitle: Ashok, a salesman, is in love with Ashoo and wants to marry her. However, things take a turn when his brother kidnaps Ashoo.

title: Kudrat
subTitle: When Chandramukhi visits Shimla, she realises that she was Paro, a girl who is raped and murdered, in her previous life. Thereafter, she decides to punish her culprits and get justice.

title: Beta Ho To Aisa
subTitle: When Laxmi's servant is killed, she brings up his son Raju with her own children. When they get involved in some shady dealings, it's up to Raju to sort out the mess his family is in.

title: Humshakal
subTitle: Ram, a poor labourer, marries Radha. One day, when their child is seriously ill, Radha arrives at her husband's place of work and is shocked to see that he is leading a dual life with another woman.

title: Barood
subTitle: Anup witnesses his father's murder as a child and travels the world to track down and exact revenge against the killers. However, a New York-based detective tries to get him arrested at any cost.

title: Barood

title: Aadat Se Majboor
subTitle: Dinanath, a devout Hindu, wishes to get his son Shankar married to Salma, an orphan who lives with them. However, Shankar's childhood sweetheart Neetu returns to his life.

title: Yeh to Kamaal Ho Gaya
subTitle: A corrupt lawyer implicates a burglar's son in a false case of murder. Eventually, the burglar kidnaps the lawyer's son and trains him in the art of crime and burglary to exact his revenge.

title: My Life My Story

title: The Train
subTitle: An honest CBI officer must investigate a series of murders on a train. However, as he makes progress in the case, he finds disturbing leads.

title: Dharam Karam
subTitle: Shankar, a criminal, switches his newborn son with another baby, hoping to provide him with a better life. Years later, Shankar's plan backfires and causes the opposite of what he intended.

title: Humjoli
subTitle: Gopaldas, a villager, dreams of becoming rich and, thus, marries Roopa, an heiress. However, his greed knows no bounds when he plots Roopa's murder to inherit her property.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.

title: Prem Kahani
subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.
